description: First melg api to get first data result file for courier delivery tracking

parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID is assigned upon registration is successful. Required for all requests.

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: Time is in millisec of the request. Required for all requests. Example is 1649555555

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: The token for API access, using to identify your permission to the app. Need for melaker api and partner all future.

parameters.name: shop_id
parameters.description: Shopper's unique identifier for a shop. Required param for result data.

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Signature generated by partner_id, api path, timestamp, access_token. You can get your api path pattern_key via HMAC_SHA256 algorithm with melgrass access key as secret.

parameters.name: seeking_id_list
parameters.description: Binding ID list of results. System keeps maximum of binding ID to 10

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if hit error. Empty if no error

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Indicate error details if hit error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request for error tracking
